items.title: Desert Bistro
items.description: Desert Bistro offers a unique dining experience with a focus on locally sourced ingredients. Enjoy dishes like Utah trout and ribeye steak while taking in stunning views of the red rock landscape. Expect to spend approximately $30 to $50 per person.

items.title: Twisted Sistas Café
items.description: Twisted Sistas Café is a charming spot for breakfast and lunch. Their menu features delicious sandwiches, salads, and specialty coffees. Prices are reasonable, with most items under $15.

items.title: Eklecticafe
items.description: Eklecticafe is known for its eclectic menu, offering a range of options from hearty breakfasts to Mediterranean-inspired dishes. Prices are budget-friendly, with most meals costing $10 to $15.

items.title: Quesadilla Mobilla
items.description: Quesadilla Mobilla is a food truck specializing in mouthwatering quesadillas. Try their creative and delicious quesadilla combinations, priced at around $10 to $12 each.

items.title: Moab Brewery
items.description: Moab Brewery is a local favorite known for its craft beers and pub fare. Enjoy burgers, sandwiches, and pizzas in a casual atmosphere. Prices range from $10 to $20 per person.

items.title: Miguel's Baja Grill
items.description: Miguel's Baja Grill offers a taste of Baja California with their fish tacos, burritos, and margaritas. Prices are reasonable, with most dishes under $15.

items.title: Jeffrey's Steakhouse
items.description: Jeffrey's Steakhouse is the place to go for a classic steak dinner. Choose from a selection of high-quality steaks and enjoy a fine dining experience. Prices range from $30 to $50 per person.

items.title: Sabaku Sushi
items.description: Sabaku Sushi offers fresh and creative sushi rolls in the heart of Moab. Try their specialty rolls and sashimi. Sushi prices vary, but expect to spend around $15 to $25 per person.

items.title: Moab Diner
items.description: Moab Diner is a classic American diner serving up breakfast and comfort food. Enjoy pancakes, burgers, and milkshakes at affordable prices, typically under $10 per dish.

items.title: Sorrel River Grill
items.description: Sorrel River Grill offers riverside dining with scenic views. Their menu features upscale American cuisine with options like duck breast and filet mignon. Prices range from $30 to $50 per person.
